{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was strictly by-- by yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were each assigned to a-- to a different place, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the idea was we're supposed to be-- this was all preparation for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were going to go on a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were very pro-Israel at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We all wanted to go to Palestine and work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, instead of working for this guy, we were going to work for ourselves, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were very idealistic, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So life goes on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said, things are getting-- the-- the-- Denmark was-- was one of the greatest country for German to be an occupation because nobody got shot there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- there was hardly any underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, occasionally a newspaper came out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you were listening to the BBC broadcast at night, which was against the law.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were miles away from any German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very rarely did we see any Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They might have come by transport on the highway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who got over to the highway, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the cities we were were little villages, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had a general store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had like a community center.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Maybe once every three months, a movie company came in and played a movie for us, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those-- you-- you lived on that farm, and you basically died on that-- you could-- I could picture myself 20 years from the day being still on that farm.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, there was no other job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to-- the idea of working seven days a week used to drive me crazy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not that we worked all day Sunday, but we had to go and milk the-- milk the cows and clean the stables.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing goes on.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
